targets.query: SELECT sum("one-minute") FROM "ru.fediq.scrapingkit.platform.QueueingActor.pulledRate" WHERE "hostname" =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s) fill(null)
SELECT sum("one-minute") FROM "ru.fediq.scrapingkit.platform.QueueingActor.drownRate" WHERE "hostname" =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s), "hostname" fill(null)
SELECT sum("one-minute") FROM "ru.fediq.scrapingkit.platform.QueueingActor.failedRate" WHERE "hostname" =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
SELECT sum("one-minute") FROM "ru.fediq.scrapingkit.platform.QueueingActor.succeedRate" WHERE "hostname" =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s) fill(null)

list.name: hostname
list.query: show tag values with key = hostname
